// the name of the file is the date of the post
// like this: YYYY-MM-DD-II
// a 4th number (II) can be given at the end to define order to multiple posts on the same date
// variables are set within the ~ marks
// status can be either PUBLISHED or DRAFT (I think this is self explanatory)
// title is obviously the title of the entry
// after the second ~ mark is the html content of the blog entry
~
status:PUBLISHED
title:New Blog System Implemented
~
This new blog system has been implemented so you can keep up to date with news from the Ancient Beast team.
